2. **`StepperItemContext`** — per-item scope: `{ step, state }` where `state` is derived as `"active" | "completed" | "pending"`

`StepperContent` uses its own `step: number` prop + reads `activeStep` from `StepperContext` (no `StepperItemContext` dependency). This lets it work anywhere inside `<Stepper>`, not just inside `<StepperItem>`.

