- `StepperTrigger` renders `{children ?? step}` — shows step number by default, custom content if provided
- `StepperSeparator.completed = activeStep > step` — separator after step N fills when moving to step N+1
- `StepperContent` returns `null` (not hidden) when inactive — keeps DOM clean
- No external dependencies — pure React + Tailwind

